/^X-Rate-Limit-Reached:\s(.*)/ FILTER domainratelimit:dummy
/^From:.*?MAILER-DAEMON.*/ REDIRECT bounces@happytailspawcare.com
/^From:.*?no-reply.*/ REDIRECT bounces@happytailspawcare.com
/^Subject:.*?Undelivered Mail Returned to Sender.*/ REDIRECT bounces@happytailspawcare.com
/^Auto-Submitted:.*?auto-replied.*/ REDIRECT bounces@happytailspawcare.com
